17. Services use UnitOfWork. Repositories use DbContext.
18. Manual mapping. No AutoMapper.
19. All AJAX calls send RequestVerificationToken header.
20. VKN/TCKN checksum validation runs server-side for every add operation.
21. Admin actions (user/role management) are audit-logged.
22. Flag actions (enable/disable/targeting) are audit-logged.
23. Audit log search and pagination MUST be fully functional.
24. On Redis failure: log warning, fall through to SQL. Never crash.
25. Kubernetes-ready: no local file system state, all shared state in Redis/PostgreSQL.
26. FastEndpoints used ONLY in Flagly.Api — not in Flagly.Web.
27. Clean Architecture: outer layers depend on inner, never reverse.
28. Each project in the solution has a single, clear responsibility.

